{
  "stem": "1680.3",
  "chunk_idx": 15,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 494.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So we came [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I look for a job.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So I got a job at Kuppenheimer as a cutter.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So I work for Kuppenheimer for 19 years.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then Kuppenheimer it was-- came in the 1960s when nobody needed any suits anymore.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Kuppenheimer was a very expensive place, one of the highest manufacturing place in Chicago, better than Hart Schaffner Marx.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So when it came to the '60s when nobody-- when everybody was wearing blue jeans and so on, so they went out of business.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They closed up.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So after this-- and I was 19 years.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I didn't have enough for pension.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I wasn't older.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I was 62 at that time when they closed it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So the union give me a job at Hart Schaffner Marx for another two years.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And after two years, this place went out of business.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "This wasn't the Hart Schaffner Marx That was the Hart Schaffner Marx, a-- a-- a-- subsidy.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Because they worked only for Sears.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "That was owned by Hart Schaffner Marx, but was called [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "It was called [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "They worked only for Sears Roebuck.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So after two years, they went out of business.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So the-- the union told me to quit.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I was 64 years old.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I got my pension at that time.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And when did you start to tell your story?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "After the movie came out.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Before the movie came-- actually, when the book came out, our rabbi in our synagogue made a Sunday breakfast for the people.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he says he's going to read some stories from from the book from the book that came out in 1982.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "When I heard this, I says, We were on When he heard this, he got very excited.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he invited Regine and Regine should come.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
